# Supabase Cloud project — Project Settings → API
# SUPABASE_URL: the Project URL (https://<ref>.supabase.co)
# SUPABASE_KEY: the anon/public key (NOT the service-role key)
# Local Node dev (`astro dev`) reads these from .env;
# local workerd (`wrangler dev`) reads .dev.vars;
# production reads Cloudflare secrets set via `wrangler secret put`.
SUPABASE_URL=###
SUPABASE_KEY=###